# PDP Next Grid System

All layout in this project uses the Figma grid:

- **Mobile** `12/12/4` — 12 columns · 12px margin · 4px gutter · 375px frame
- **Desktop** `24/20/8` — 24 columns · 20px margin · 8px gutter · 1440px frame

Use `@/components/grid/page-grid` (`PageShell`, `PageGrid`, `GridItem`). Do not use arbitrary page padding or custom column counts.

Full reference: `docs/design-system/grid.md` · Skill: `.cursor/skills/pdp-grid-system/SKILL.md`

## Typography

All UI text: **Helvetica Neue LT Pro**. See `docs/design-system/typography.md`.

## Icons

All icons: **Google Material Symbols** via `@/components/icons/material-icon`. See `docs/design-system/icons.md`.
